node.text:
For the first time since missing his penalty in the Euro 2020 final, @bukayosaka87 returned to Wembley last night 🏟

On his 20th birthday, he scored the 4️⃣th goal for 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿 against Andorra 🥳

After the game, Saka received a very loud ovation from the stadium after giving his shirt to a kid in the stands and he was even named Man of the Match 👏🌶
